Until Verbed Method Step.

This recipe tests the "until verbed" method step. Verb can be one of a number
of possible supported verbs.

Ingredients.
100 g flour
500 g butter
3 onions

Method.
Sift the flour until sifted.
Rub the butter until melted.
Heat the butter until melted.
Melt the butter until heated.
Cook the onions until caramelised.
Caramelise the onions until softened.
Cook until caramelised.
Heat until melted.

Serves 1.
